author: Cleo Abram
description:
Did you know scientists discovered that Earth and our solar system are inside a weird bubble in space?

Our galaxy is normally super crowded with dense clouds of gas and dust. What you’re seeing is based on real data from the Gaia space telescope! Here’s what’s odd… 

These visuals are from the American Museum of Natural History’s incredible show, Encounters in the Milky Way. It’s incredible. Go watch it!

#shorts #history #sky #timelapse #animation #sun
title: We’re In A Weird Space Bubble
